{"tid":2064183,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"無綫小花邱晴離巢向外闖    曾月入5萬變「一騷藝人合約」","createTime":"2020-06-14T15:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T09:23:16.000Z","uid":257448,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dafd04405a6cebdaf589bb8d30b4f7a037b9c5b3","tid":2064183,"uid":257448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:21:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/無綫小花邱晴離巢向外闖-曾月入-5-萬變一騷藝人合約-064926942.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E5%B0%8F%E8%8A%B1%E9%82%B1%E6%99%B4%E9%9B%A2%E5%B7%A2%E5%90%91%E5%A4%96%E9%97%96-%E6%9B%BE%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5-5-%E8%90%AC%E8%AE%8A%E4%B8%80%E9%A8%B7%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84-064926942.html&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8s%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=abb4dd12\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/無綫小花邱晴離巢向外闖-曾月入-5-萬變一騷藝人合約-064926942.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TbqWnecdzCGKzsCn69zYrg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTA4MDtoPTcyMQ--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/1e3ed2e0-a946-11ea-b2fc-2032dec2f932\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTbqWnecdzCGKzsCn69zYrg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTA4MDtoPTcyMQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2F1e3ed2e0-a946-11ea-b2fc-2032dec2f932&h=e24c9f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無綫鬧演員荒已經唔係新鮮事，今年都有唔少演員相繼離巢向外闖，最新就有邱晴（Mandy）。今年只得20歲嘅邱晴，2017年參選香港小姐後入行，雖然冇獲得任何名次，但都成功入無綫做藝人。青春無敵嘅Mandy憑住可愛甜美嘅樣及索爆身材，成功俘虜一班粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n喺入行後，邱晴主要擔任兒童節目《Think Big天地》主持，亦有做過 《美女廚房3》嘅美女學徒。另外，佢都有客串唔同劇集，例如《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》中「傻強」女朋友Dorothy，係無綫等上位小花之一。不過自5月起《Think Big天地》突然見唔到佢，原來佢由「親生女」轉簽為「一騷藝人合約」。<br />\n<br />\n邱晴接受傳媒訪問時，話想試吓唔同發展，喺網絡媒體可以分享佢嘅日常生活，又可以多啲同粉絲互動。不過佢有提及現況同收入都同以前有分別，喺無綫有固定收入，仲試過有幾個月有5萬蚊左右，又可以買奢侈品畀媽咪。但而家就好唔同，雖然轉咗約，公司都有job俾佢做，不過就要慳啲洗，同埋諗點樣賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n離巢後，Mandy轉由樂宜（Lokyii）個經理人幫手管理工作，Mandy表示唔係同樂宜以及浜崎真緒一樣做夜場DJ，佢會整個Channel同小朋友互動，一齊玩吓或者一齊唱吓歌。Mandy而家就不停學習充實自己，學吓唱歌、煮食，打機、同埋做運動等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aJZnhYTxkWRyXFXkt9eRpQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTA4MDtoPTc3MQ--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/27914c60-a946-11ea-979b-f846f5b65b1e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FaJZnhYTxkWRyXFXkt9eRpQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTA4MDtoPTc3MQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2F27914c60-a946-11ea-979b-f846f5b65b1e&h=b21afa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gSzJyMimH91uNzoHqeT6Eg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/3009b990-a946-11ea-bbfd-eceb84e381e4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FgSzJyMimH91uNzoHqeT6Eg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2F3009b990-a946-11ea-bbfd-eceb84e381e4&h=adc1ce39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qW.KOfDE6xJ1tTpANe784g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTA4MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/450baf60-a946-11ea-bf9d-578a7bff86ef\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FqW.KOfDE6xJ1tTpANe784g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTA4MDtoPTcyMA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2F450baf60-a946-11ea-bf9d-578a7bff86ef&h=a9317919&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"287c1276dd303e3bf4a67ac230e87964a5ff89c2","tid":2064183,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:22